{"tid":796351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"定期覺得自己on9到無藥醫","createTime":"2018-08-27T17:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T04:11:38.000Z","uid":202581,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98b013f330d9055fd04009381ca146e6a532da4f","tid":796351,"uid":202581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成撚日做埋啲on9嘢 搞到自己都覺得煩<br />\n一係就成日望隔離舖條仔 request完人地accept完我ig inbox佢無理我之後就unfoll<br />\n一係就同屋企人嘈交 自己一條友出去頹咗一日 返黎先發現無人被影響心情<br />\n一係就為自己莫名其妙既執著 而堅持要講自己既睇法 最後可能就搞到老母唔舒服唔開心<br />\n好想打爆自己 突然消失就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159a0174df117038b0e405c42ce945674886600e","tid":796351,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:38:13.000Z","msg":"this"},{"pid":"8ccf097d19263704386599873bcacfda5f9e8e56","tid":796351,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"終於意識到無人care？<br />\n唔好以為好似小學雞咁發脾氣 扭計會有人理。"},{"pid":"3e59559e43b6448a278f57f143df089b008f2047","tid":796351,"uid":202581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccf097d19263704386599873bcacfda5f9e8e56","tid":796351,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"終於意識到無人care？<br />\n唔好以為好似小學雞咁發脾氣 扭計會有人理。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:52:50.000Z","msg":"從來都無對人發過脾氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上嚟講兩句姐"},{"pid":"cb0a74a1f5366b6b48f0a39d0427fba9fe5a39a3","tid":796351,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e59559e43b6448a278f57f143df089b008f2047","tid":796351,"uid":202581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccf097d19263704386599873bcacfda5f9e8e56","tid":796351,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"終於意識到無人care？<br />\n唔好以為好似小學雞咁發脾氣 扭計會有人理。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:52:50.000Z","msg":"從來都無對人發過脾氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上嚟講兩句姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T21:08:59.000Z","msg":"inbox人，人地唔理。成件事好正常。唔試點知人地理唔理你？唔理咪unfollow 廢事晒氣。<br />\n駁老母都無問題。覺得自己啱嘅話無必要去理人。問題係你為咩而駁，又會唔會明知最後唔會有結論都嘈落去。<br />\n<br />\n「一係就同屋企人嘈交 自己一條友出去頹咗一日 返黎先發現無人被影響心情」<br />\n<br />\n講到好似出去頹係想返到去會有人被影響心情噉，都唔知你想點。<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得自己成日煩無謂嘢，噉或者係因為你無認真嘢好煩，亦有可能你唔去諗認真嘢。<br />\n<br />\n又話個男仔唔理你，又話屋企人無被你影響心情，搞到好似你好缺乏關懷咁。事實係呢個世界 no one gives a flying fuck. 如人飲水，冷暖自知。與其在意人，不如諗下自己係到做緊咩，短期可以做咩，長期可以做咩。"},{"pid":"a287bc834270aadb170b25e774c7c89e5f0988ec","tid":796351,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T21:10:11.000Z","msg":"開個噉嘅post都睇得出"},{"pid":"946b9cfb1187cb1217bc52e91646ab2f642e5444","tid":796351,"uid":22830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T22:04:39.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1829946d6c5fe8beca8def35df34df847c8fe726","tid":796351,"uid":202581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946b9cfb1187cb1217bc52e91646ab2f642e5444","tid":796351,"uid":22830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T22:04:39.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:41:59.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後都唔喺連登卡開呢啲post樂 開完仲灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b14076ab705f88f23a0c6d001a46fc6a1645a1","tid":796351,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n<br />\n連開呢個post都係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係冇藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmo